description:
The Sitaware C2 system (HC2 6.18) will be used during CWIX execution. This means the exchange of data as follows:

<u>eXamination</u>
* SPO-289: Provide the ability to exchange ORBAT, TASKORG, plan and orders bi-directionally between OPCIS-TACCIS and TACCIS-TACCIS;	
* SPO-310: Provide ability to exchange situation awareness information from OPCIS to TACCIS.
<u>eXercise</u>
* Exchange of air picture (Link16);
* Exchange of Maritime picture (OTH-G);
* Exchange of Land picture;
* Exchange of FFT;

This objective includes tests using Content-Item and Composite entities. Tests will be conducted to validate:
*producer/consumer implementations;
*the operational impact caused by ignoring these entities.
